      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "As a third check, you can add <code>Mockito.verify(mockObject, Mockito.times(2)).testMethod(Mockito.any());</code>. Together those checks guarantee that the method is called exactly once with each argument."
