    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use <code>Mockito.atLeastOnce()</code> which allows Mockito to pass the test even if that mockObject will be called many times.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Mockito.verify(mockObject, Mockito.atLeastOnce()).testMethod(Mockito.eq(1));\n\nMockito.verify(mockObject, Mockito.atLeastOnce()).testMethod(Mockito.eq(2));\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
